      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "whom she bare unto Saul, Armoni and Mephibosheth; of whom we read nowhere else; after the name of the latter, it is probable, Jonathan's son was called, before mentioned: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
